{"tid":1003294,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"今日搭巴士，個細路一上車就大叫施施縮縮","createTime":"2019-01-31T14:00:57.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-01T04:00:10.000Z","uid":35324,"like":4,"dislike":14,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"c38e6adbc5cbf0da6826b1011a24f8ea953285af","tid":1003294,"uid":35324,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-31T14:00:57.000Z","msg":"我心諗，啲10後真係好冇禮貌又冇家教<br />\n我係毒呀，關你撚事咩，使唔使咁大聲鬧我施施縮縮<br />\n<br />\n我即刻睥撚實個細路<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n佢老闆，眼尾都唔望下我，真係好冇禮貌<br />\n<br />\n我睥咗兩秒，佢又細細聲講多句施施縮縮<br />\n我今次真係忍唔住，嬲到大嗌<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">「關你撚事呀！」</span><br />\n<br />\n個細路同佢老豆都嚇咗一跳<br />\n我好想笑，但為咗保持威嚴，唯有忍住<br />\n哈，終於可以教訓下啲死𡃁仔！<br />\n<br />\n呢個時候，佢老豆細細聲同個細路講"},{"pid":"f6402c9163b54fcbe86804f6a80bf5cf4726fc7b","tid":1003294,"uid":35324,"like":4,"dislike":21,"score":-17,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-31T14:01:17.000Z","msg":"係司機叔叔，唔係施施叔叔呀"},{"pid":"6dde76d2a016c95bd5fc4c462b83e3a466a85ae4","tid":1003294,"uid":38177,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-31T14:02:24.000Z","msg":"閱"},{"pid":"b96ca174939f6e0304c093695e5a658974d910f6","tid":1003294,"uid":5205,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-31T15:19:33.000Z","msg":"見到樓主眼神制敵"},{"pid":"14a14c30e02839900d3423da1e3b8e21f241911e","tid":1003294,"uid":35324,"like":3,"dislike":3,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-31T17:41:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 咁撚好笑都冇人"},{"pid":"e1b0d5143478b0c6f1e04cb78926f1003bf81266","tid":1003294,"uid":35324,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-31T17:41:30.000Z","msg":"聽日再推"},{"pid":"4ea99032682f2ce1f0435ed75a114fb4f21ce6e4","tid":1003294,"uid":220479,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-31T17:50:42.000Z","msg":"1/10<br />\n1分同情分<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d56afcafb1a12c8f174865eed5618dc3004